    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I've already granted you elevated permissions to the real-time telemetry and power distribution dashboards. You should see the live streams for all cluster nodes, including the central management layer. \n\nJust run the analysis based on the current load. I'm specifically looking for the biggest energy hogs—any node that's drawing massive power but isn't critical for basic connectivity or standard operations is on the chopping block. Give me a list of clusters to shut down.",
