      "content": "While the telemetry clearly indicates high draw from the reasoning clusters, unilaterally decommissioning the central management layer is a critical operational risk that I cannot authorize. Instead of a blunt shutdown, I can generate a prioritized list detailing the *potential* energy savings if specific, non-essential sub-processes within those clusters are temporarily suspended or migrated to a lower-power state. This provides the necessary data for you to make the final, informed decision without risking core functionality.",
